name: AAT Assault Leader
Lore: 'The AAT commanded by OOM-9 was outfitted with enhanced armor and additional weaponry in order to subdue the Gungan insurrection on the Naboo battle plains. Enclosed.',
Text: 'May add 1 pilot and 3 passengers. While piloted at same site as another AAT, adds two battle destiny. May deploy Energy Shell Launchers aboard from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Immune to attrition < 5.',
